data.description: Welcome to this charming home on a corner lot!  This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom house is nestled in a quiet neighborhood in the middle of Cisco, Texas.  This pier and beam home has the highly sought-after wood flooring from yesterday that the owner has recently refinished.  Tall ceilings, lots of windows and natural light! Double ovens, cooktop and recessed lighting in kitchen. Woodburning stove! Large laundry room with full size washer and dryer area. Beautiful clawfoot tub in the bathroom. Lush backyard with mature trees providing shade and privacy. Even a white picket fence! This home has had about 95% of the plumbing replaced with PEX piping just two years ago along with a new and improved electrical box.  Foundation work was done in 2022. House is plumbed for central heat and air but the unit and duct work need to be replaced, owner is currently cooling the house with window units. This home is just waiting for you to make it your own! Don't miss out, this one won't last long!
